## Implementation Details

### Structure Before Fix
```tsx
<Widget>
  <div className="flex-1 overflow-auto p-4"> {/* Scrollable */}
    <div className="calendar-widget h-full flex flex-col">
      <div className="calendar-nav">  {/* ❌ SCROLLS */}
