```

**Problem:** The entire calendar-widget was in the Widget's scrollable content area, so navigation + views scrolled together.

### Structure After Fix
```tsx
<Widget>
  <div className="flex-1 overflow-auto"> {/* No padding */}
    <div className="calendar-widget h-full flex flex-col">
      {/* FROZEN SECTION */}
      <div className="flex-shrink-0 px-4 pt-4"> {/* ✅ FROZEN */}
