        MonthView / WeekView / DayView / AgendaView
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Widget>
```

**Solution:** Calendar component now has two sections:
1. **Frozen navigation** (`flex-shrink-0 px-4 pt-4`) - Always visible
2. **Scrollable grid** (`flex-1 overflow-y-auto px-4 pb-4`) - Scrolls internally

