## Technical Details

### Why This Fix Works

**Flexbox Layout:**
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Calendar Widget (h-full flex col)  │
│ ┌─────────────────────────────────┐ │
│ │ Frozen Nav (flex-shrink-0)      │ │ ← Always visible
│ │ px-4 pt-4                        │ │
│ │ Previous | Month | Views | Next  │ │
│ └─────────────────────────────────┘ │
│ ┌─────────────────────────────────┐ │
│ │ Scrollable Grid (flex-1)        │ │ ← Fills space
│ │ overflow-y-auto px-4 pb-4       │ │ ← Scrolls
│ │ [Month/Week/Day/List View]      │ │
│ │ ...                             │ │
│ │ ...                             │ │
│ └─────────────────────────────────┘ │
└─────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Height Distribution:**
- Calendar widget: `h-full` (fills Widget content area)
- Frozen section: `flex-shrink-0` (natural height, doesn't shrink)
- Scrollable section: `flex-1` (fills remaining space = total height - frozen height)
- `overflow-y-auto` enables scrolling when content exceeds available height

